{"tid":443670,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"同朋友打機既態度","createTime":"2017-10-21T18:22:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-21T19:20:44.000Z","uid":8773,"like":5,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d4952150b63883436829a5ce3cb2badc1307e958","tid":443670,"uid":8773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T18:22:54.000Z","msg":"最緊同班朋友打pro club，好難先升到上去<br />\n成日鳩叫波，又唔識傳，係咁死扭，亂鳩咁踢<br />\n打到好撚燥，燥完之後又諗都係打機啫<br />\n又同時都想大家打好啲，一齊贏波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n正評-打機想贏好正常，同垃圾隊友預左燥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n負評-打機輸贏好少事，最撚緊要係一齊玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34f5efa3161b5a8c9d5471671c1af9748b6c9bd3","tid":443670,"uid":26507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T18:25:02.000Z","msg":"我都係咁，下下call波，其他人玩撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f0a1e30a79df37b638faa625acbcc98edfd6cfc","tid":443670,"uid":8773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T18:28:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都係咁，下下call波，其他人玩撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n會忍唔住屌左幾句，真心唔想輸波<br />\n仲要唔止輸一球，係比人大炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79080aa5e9f7adac146409cc2c9577745c74f130","tid":443670,"uid":8773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T18:30:52.000Z","msg":"雖然諗番都係覺得一班人打機最緊要開心<br />\n但鋪鋪都輸點開心繼續打落去<br />\n男人打機梗係想贏啦屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1fde639a6bdd560327e49fca87cb23dcc4226e6","tid":443670,"uid":68014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T18:31:50.000Z","msg":"呢個真係不解既問題黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <b